                    both guests and hosts. Enjoy a hassle-free stay with StayEase, where comfort meets convenience.</p>
            </div>
            <div  style="height: 100%;">
                <img  src="https://cdn.b12.io/client_media/ZVAXFXpm/5e31b70a-5bee-11ef-89c7-0242ac110002-jpg-hero_image.jpeg" style="height: 100%;" alt="StayEase Image">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="c3">
            <div class="inner-c3">
            <h5>Our Services</h5>
            <h4>Explore what we offer</h4>
            <div >
                <div >
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560114928-40a38d486b33?ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8c2VhcmNofDI0fHxob3RlbHxlbnwwfHx8fDE2OTIzNjYwMzk&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&w=1000&q=80" alt="Service 1">
                    <h6>Hotel Booking</h6>
                    <p>Book hotels at your favorite destinations with ease and convenience through our platform.</p>
                </div>
                <div >
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600932711714-1fef7c08525a?ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8c2VhcmNofDJ8fGhvdGVsfGVufDB8fHx8MTY5MjM2NjA0Mw&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&w=1000&q=80" alt="Service 2">
                    <h6>Property Listing</h6>
                    <p>List your property with StayEase to reach more potential guests and manage bookings seamlessly.</p>
                </div>
                <div >
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1602010121807-07d90394e4c3?ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8c2VhcmNofDV8fGhvdGVsfGVufDB8fHx8MTY5MjM2NjA0Mw&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&w=1000&q=80" style="object-fit: cover;" alt="Service 3">
                    <h6>Customer Support</h6>
                    <p>We're here to help with any questions or issues you might have, 24/7.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="c4">
            <form action="">
                <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5"></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Send</button>
            </form>
            <div>
                <h5>Contact Information</h5>
                <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> 123 StayEase St, Pune, MH, India</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +91 98765 43210</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> contact@stayease.com</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
